Install
--------
For building the source the following development packaged are needed:
*) libmapi-dev
   for native access to MS Exchange
*) kdepim-dev
   for access to akonadi and KDE's PIM suite

Usage
-----
Adding an Exchange calendar:
Open "kontact", switch to the calendar view. Right-click in the lower left list and select "Add Calendar..."

Adding contacts from the Exchange Global Address List:
Open "kontact", switch to the contacts view. Right-click in the left list and select "Add Address Book..."

